description: Reserved Matters Application in relation to Plots G, J and L (Phase 2) of the Grahame Park Stage B pursuant to conditions 7, 10, 12, 28 and 44 attached to hybrid planning permission 19/5493/OUT (dated 31st July 2020). This application seeks approval of details relating to layout, scale, appearance, access and landscaping for the residential mixed use development comprising 442 residential units across three development plots and five blocks (G1, J1/J2, J3, L1 and L2) ranging from ground plus 7 storeys to ground plus 10 storeys in height, flexible commercial space (Use Class E), a housing office (Use Class E), childrens nursery (Use Class E), public open space and public realm, car parking spaces, cycle parking spaces, refuse storage space, construction of part of Bristol Avenue and other associated works. The application is accompanied by an Environmental Statement of Compliance.
